Package: COSTsim
Title: Simulation package for COST.
Version: 1.1
Date: 2009
Author: COST Team and various contributors.
Description: This package contains functions for simulating real trip/haul population and 
	'clData', 'csData' and 	'ceData' COST objects from the simulated population.
	 Functions to compare the accuracy, bias and precision of the different estimation methods 
	 in COSTdbe and COSTmbe packages are also available. It can be used to assessed optimum 
	  sample size and design.
Depends: R(>= 2.8.1), COSTcore, COSTdbe, COSTmbe
Maintainer: Dorleta Garcia <dgarcia@azti.es>
License: GPL 2 or above
LazyLoad: Yes
LazyData: Yes

